name: SEO Keywords Suggestions
title: SEO Keywords Suggestions

api_list.name: Get Keyword Suggestions
api_list.description:
This endpoint works with updated Google keywords information. Once requested, it will return 100 keyword suggestions, related to the given keyword.

Each record will also have information about SEO competition (between 0 and 1), CPC, monthly search volume, and historical monthly searches over the last year.
